1167
00:49:02,039 --> 00:49:04,542
mother and sister and brother,

1168
00:49:04,542 --> 00:49:06,277
knowing I might never see them

1169
00:49:06,277 --> 00:49:07,611
again.

1170
00:49:10,281 --> 00:49:13,484
Nanalokay,

1171
00:49:13,484 --> 00:49:16,187
sister Agay,

1172
00:49:16,187 --> 00:49:18,355
brother Lassar.

1173
00:49:21,458 --> 00:49:25,229
So many years have intervened.

1174
00:49:25,229 --> 00:49:29,533
So many words.

1175
00:49:32,736 --> 00:49:35,105
Today, what tortures

1176
00:49:35,105 --> 00:49:37,107
of loneliness.

1177
00:49:44,682 --> 00:49:46,484
From the Calcutta Corporation,

1178
00:49:46,484 --> 00:49:48,385
they will give us land

1179
00:49:48,385 --> 00:49:49,587
and build a small school house

1180
00:49:49,587 --> 00:49:51,555
when we have 100 pupils.

1181
00:49:51,555 --> 00:49:52,756
It won't be long now.

1182
00:49:52,756 --> 00:49:54,225
Meanwhile, I think we should

1183
00:49:54,225 --> 00:49:55,459
open a school for only

1184
00:49:55,459 --> 00:49:56,360
Muslim girls.

1185
00:49:56,360 --> 00:49:57,661
(truck horn honks)

1186
00:49:57,661 --> 00:49:59,063
(shouting)

1187
00:50:04,134 --> 00:50:06,136
Sounds like trouble, Sister.

1188
00:50:06,136 --> 00:50:08,205
(horn honks)

1189
00:50:13,277 --> 00:50:16,747
(crowd shouting)

1190
00:50:19,817 --> 00:50:21,518
It's for your own good!

1191
00:50:21,518 --> 00:50:23,387
Don't you understand?!

1192
00:50:23,387 --> 00:50:25,623
The authorities don't want you

1193
00:50:25,623 --> 00:50:28,092
to live in filth anymore!

1194
00:50:28,092 --> 00:50:30,427
Is this your doing, Sister?

1195
00:50:30,427 --> 00:50:31,328
No!

1196
00:50:31,328 --> 00:50:33,397
Then you have to stop them.

1197
00:50:33,397 --> 00:50:34,765
Will they listen to me?

1198
00:50:34,765 --> 00:50:36,500
It might make things worse.

1199
00:50:36,500 --> 00:50:37,534
Please.

1200
00:50:37,534 --> 00:50:40,037
(shouting)

1201
00:50:44,241 --> 00:50:46,544
Hey, you!

1202
00:50:46,544 --> 00:50:47,811
You're obstructing

1203
00:50:47,811 --> 00:50:49,146
municipal workers!

1204
00:50:49,146 --> 00:50:51,248
Get down!

1205
00:50:51,248 --> 00:50:52,816
Get down, or I'll arrest you!

1206
00:50:59,723 --> 00:51:00,758
Who are you?

1207
00:51:00,758 --> 00:51:02,526
Sister Teresa

1208
00:51:02,526 --> 00:51:03,861
from the Loreto Order.

1209
00:51:03,861 --> 00:51:06,263
I work here in Moti Jihl.

1210
00:51:06,263 --> 00:51:08,399
In this slum?

1211
00:51:08,399 --> 00:51:09,300
With these hooligans?

1212
00:51:09,300 --> 00:51:09,967
These people are

1213
00:51:09,967 --> 00:51:12,503
my sisters and my brothers.

1214
00:51:12,503 --> 00:51:13,571
We share the slum

1215
00:51:13,571 --> 00:51:15,873
with the rats.

1216
00:51:15,873 --> 00:51:17,341
She's not one of us!

1217
00:51:17,341 --> 00:51:19,176
Take her away with you!

1218
00:51:19,176 --> 00:51:20,878
We don't want a white woman!

1219
00:51:20,878 --> 00:51:23,514
Did you hear that?

1220
00:51:23,514 --> 00:51:24,548
Get out of the way

1221
00:51:24,548 --> 00:51:25,582
before you get hurt.

1222
00:51:25,582 --> 00:51:26,717
Their only fault

1223
00:51:26,717 --> 00:51:28,218
is that they're poor.

1224
00:51:28,218 --> 00:51:29,219
Poverty is an accident,

1225
00:51:29,219 --> 00:51:30,220
it tells you nothing about

1226
00:51:30,220 --> 00:51:30,888
a person.

1227
00:51:30,888 --> 00:51:31,789
I don't have the time

1228
00:51:31,789 --> 00:51:32,656
to be preached.

1229
00:51:32,656 --> 00:51:33,724
This man there,

1230
00:51:33,724 --> 00:51:34,792
Manik Sulamin,

1231
00:51:34,792 --> 00:51:35,859
the man you want to arrest.

1232
00:51:35,859 --> 00:51:39,163
He has four sons and a wife.

1233
00:51:39,163 --> 00:51:40,531
He keeps them alive by salvaging

1234
00:51:40,531 --> 00:51:42,733
garbage from this dump.

1235
00:51:42,733 --> 00:51:44,501
What will happen to his family

1236
00:51:44,501 --> 00:51:45,502
if you arrest him?

1237
00:51:45,502 --> 00:51:47,237
City officials have ordered

1238
00:51:47,237 --> 00:51:48,272
this operation.

1239
00:51:48,272 --> 00:51:49,206
It's my job to make--

1240
00:51:49,206 --> 00:51:50,574
Have the city officials asked

1241
00:51:50,574 --> 00:51:51,842
these people what they want?

1242
00:51:51,842 --> 00:51:53,711
No! No!

1243
00:51:53,711 --> 00:51:55,612
If they're so eager to help,

1244
00:51:55,612 --> 00:51:56,480
why don't they try

1245
00:51:56,480 --> 00:51:57,348
and find a way to bring

1246
00:51:57,348 --> 00:51:59,183
clean water to Moti Jihl?

1247
00:51:59,183 --> 00:52:00,284
What about those toilets

1248
00:52:00,284 --> 00:52:01,285
that are supposed to be cleaned

1249
00:52:01,285 --> 00:52:02,853
once a week?

1250
00:52:02,853 --> 00:52:03,921
The sanitation workers

1251
00:52:03,921 --> 00:52:05,189
never come.

1252
00:52:05,189 --> 00:52:06,657
No one can go near those places,

1253
00:52:06,657 --> 00:52:07,891
they're smelling so badly.

1254
00:52:07,891 --> 00:52:09,326
Some people use the gutters.

1255
00:52:09,326 --> 00:52:11,328
It's not my responsibility.

1256
00:52:11,328 --> 00:52:12,196
Then make it

1257
00:52:12,196 --> 00:52:12,863
your responsibility.

1258
00:52:15,599 --> 00:52:17,301
Please, Mr. Commissioner.

1259
00:52:17,301 --> 00:52:19,303
I ask you on behalf

1260
00:52:19,303 --> 00:52:21,438
of the people of Moti Jihl,

1261
00:52:21,438 --> 00:52:23,741
go to your city authorities

1262
00:52:23,741 --> 00:52:24,975
and ask them to cancel

1263
00:52:24,975 --> 00:52:26,243
these orders.

1264
00:52:26,243 --> 00:52:27,878
Yeah! Yeah!

1265
00:52:27,878 --> 00:52:30,347
Yes! Yes!

1266
00:52:30,347 --> 00:52:33,517
(crowd shouting)

1267
00:52:34,385 --> 00:52:36,220
(camera shutter clicks)

1268
00:52:41,658 --> 00:52:42,860
For the safety of the men,

1269
00:52:42,860 --> 00:52:44,495
this operation is discontinued

1270
00:52:44,495 --> 00:52:45,496
for now.

1271
00:52:45,496 --> 00:52:47,498
Thank you, Commissioner.

1272
00:52:47,498 --> 00:52:49,900
(cheering)

1273
00:52:49,900 --> 00:52:51,235
You haven't heard

1274
00:52:51,235 --> 00:52:52,669
the last of this.

1275
00:52:54,338 --> 00:52:57,307
(cheering)

1276
00:53:03,747 --> 00:53:05,716
Sister.

1277
00:53:05,716 --> 00:53:08,552
I was wrong about you, Sister.

1278
00:53:08,552 --> 00:53:09,887
No time for apologies.

1279
00:53:09,887 --> 00:53:12,289
We have much work to do.

1280
00:53:14,324 --> 00:53:16,193
(cheering)

1281
00:53:20,998 --> 00:53:22,366
(scoffs)

1282
00:53:22,366 --> 00:53:23,400
Well, I'll be.

1283
00:53:25,769 --> 00:53:27,304
If it isn't that pushy

1284
00:53:27,304 --> 00:53:29,339
little headmistress again.

1285
00:53:29,339 --> 00:53:31,708
Now, she's working in the slums.

1286
00:53:33,477 --> 00:53:35,546
Harry Harper,

1287
00:53:35,546 --> 00:53:38,482
this may interest you.

1288
00:53:39,750 --> 00:53:40,617
Now that you've

1289
00:53:40,617 --> 00:53:41,485
finished school,

1290
00:53:41,485 --> 00:53:42,453
will you go to Europe

1291
00:53:42,453 --> 00:53:43,520
with your mother, Sunita?

1292
00:53:43,520 --> 00:53:45,622
Perhaps. I first want to

1293
00:53:45,622 --> 00:53:46,757
visit Sister Teresa.

1294
00:53:46,757 --> 00:53:49,426
Ah, well, tell her

1295
00:53:49,426 --> 00:53:50,461
we miss her.

1296
00:53:50,461 --> 00:53:52,529
Good luck.

1297
00:53:52,529 --> 00:53:53,831
God bless you.

1298
00:53:53,831 --> 00:53:55,666
Thank you, Sister.

1299
00:53:57,701 --> 00:53:58,569
Tell Sister Teresa that

1300
00:53:58,569 --> 00:53:59,837
we want her to come back.

1301
00:53:59,837 --> 00:54:00,704
Tell her that.

1302
00:54:00,704 --> 00:54:01,839
They won't let her back.

1303
00:54:01,839 --> 00:54:02,973
They say she's walking around

1304
00:54:02,973 --> 00:54:04,575
Calcutta like a beggar woman.

1305
00:54:04,575 --> 00:54:05,809
They say she's cracked.

1306
00:54:05,809 --> 00:54:06,844
Oh, shut up.

1307
00:54:06,844 --> 00:54:07,778
Is it true?

1308
00:54:07,778 --> 00:54:08,745
That's not true.

1309
00:54:08,745 --> 00:54:11,381
I want to see for myself.

1310
00:54:11,381 --> 00:54:13,617
If I could, I'd run away

1311
00:54:13,617 --> 00:54:14,485
and go and work with her.

1312
00:54:14,485 --> 00:54:15,652
(laughing)

1313
00:54:15,652 --> 00:54:17,654
You better finish school first,

1314
00:54:17,654 --> 00:54:18,589
Maria.

1315
00:54:18,589 --> 00:54:20,457
Just one year to go. Bye.

1316
00:54:20,457 --> 00:54:22,659
Bye.

1317
00:54:25,863 --> 00:54:28,332
Five more deaths,

1318
00:54:28,332 --> 00:54:29,867
we are caring for 16 men,

1319
00:54:29,867 --> 00:54:32,536
13 women, and six children.

1320
00:54:32,536 --> 00:54:34,738
More come every day.

1321
00:54:34,738 --> 00:54:38,442
(knocking)

1322
00:54:40,544 --> 00:54:41,578
Who is it?

1323
00:54:41,578 --> 00:54:43,714
Sunita.

1324
00:54:47,784 --> 00:54:50,888
Sunita!

1325
00:54:50,888 --> 00:54:53,023
How did you find me?

1326
00:54:53,023 --> 00:54:55,058
What are you doing here?

1327
00:54:55,058 --> 00:54:57,427
Father gave me your address.

1328
00:54:57,427 --> 00:55:00,097
I've come to work with you.

1329
00:55:00,097 --> 00:55:02,833
Oh!

1330
00:55:02,833 --> 00:55:04,635
(gasping)

1331
00:55:06,837 --> 00:55:08,005
This is the first time

1332
00:55:08,005 --> 00:55:08,972
in my life I've seen you

1333
00:55:08,972 --> 00:55:11,308
at a loss for words.

1334
00:55:21,985 --> 00:55:24,021
The Sister of Calcutta

1335
00:55:24,021 --> 00:55:25,556
to help her poor.

1336
00:55:25,556 --> 00:55:27,391
Ah, morning, Mr. Goma.

1337
00:55:27,391 --> 00:55:29,059
Good morning, good morning.

1338
00:55:29,059 --> 00:55:30,427
The Bengalis have a custom

1339
00:55:30,427 --> 00:55:31,762
of setting aside a cup of rice

1340
00:55:31,762 --> 00:55:32,863
for a beggar.

1341
00:55:32,863 --> 00:55:34,898
Sister Teresa has inspired

1342
00:55:34,898 --> 00:55:37,067
our congregation to practice it

1343
00:55:37,067 --> 00:55:38,602
liberally.

1344
00:55:42,506 --> 00:55:44,841
Maria, what are you

1345
00:55:44,841 --> 00:55:47,144
doing here?

1346
00:55:47,144 --> 00:55:48,946
I have come to help.

1347
00:55:48,946 --> 00:55:50,981
But what about school?

1348
00:55:50,981 --> 00:55:52,115
What will your parents say?

1349
00:55:52,115 --> 00:55:55,152
They want me to get married.

1350
00:55:55,152 --> 00:55:56,753
But I want to be a nun.

1351
00:55:56,753 --> 00:55:58,021
Please, Sister Teresa.

1352
00:55:58,021 --> 00:55:59,723
Let me stay with you.

1353
00:55:59,723 --> 00:56:01,992
We can't, Sister.

1354
00:56:01,992 --> 00:56:03,560
She hasn't completed high school

1355
00:56:03,560 --> 00:56:05,128
yet.

1356
00:56:05,128 --> 00:56:08,031
But I want to help the poor.

1357
00:56:10,434 --> 00:56:12,569
Come to Moti Jihl.

1358
00:56:12,569 --> 00:56:13,804
Come and see.

1359
00:56:13,804 --> 00:56:15,739
Come and see if this the life

1360
00:56:15,739 --> 00:56:16,840
you really want.

1361
00:56:16,840 --> 00:56:20,377
(chanting)

1362
00:56:37,060 --> 00:56:38,495
(coughing)

1363
00:56:40,197 --> 00:56:42,799
(people groaning)

1364
00:56:46,603 --> 00:56:48,672
Come.

1365
00:56:49,740 --> 00:56:51,541
Let me show you what to do,

1366
00:56:51,541 --> 00:56:54,244
come.

1367
00:56:54,244 --> 00:56:56,913
There are four of them now.

1368
00:56:56,913 --> 00:56:58,148
It's outrageous.

1369
00:56:58,148 --> 00:56:59,850
Sit, both of you.

1370
00:57:02,119 --> 00:57:03,120
Do you realize

1371
00:57:03,120 --> 00:57:04,221
what it looks like?

1372
00:57:04,221 --> 00:57:06,056
A group of young Indian girls

1373
00:57:06,056 --> 00:57:07,591
from the best families

1374
00:57:07,591 --> 00:57:08,992
running around Calcutta

1375
00:57:08,992 --> 00:57:10,227
unsupervised.

1376
00:57:10,227 --> 00:57:11,561
But they are hardly

1377
00:57:11,561 --> 00:57:12,262
unsupervised.

1378
00:57:12,262 --> 00:57:13,730
Sister Teresa is their

1379
00:57:13,730 --> 00:57:14,598
headmistress.

1380
00:57:14,598 --> 00:57:15,499
She knows how to handle--

1381
00:57:15,499 --> 00:57:18,769
I agree with the Archbishop.

1382
00:57:18,769 --> 00:57:20,537
It's putting our whole order

1383
00:57:20,537 --> 00:57:21,672
into a bad light.

1384
00:57:21,672 --> 00:57:23,173
I'm putting a stop to this

1385
00:57:23,173 --> 00:57:24,808
right now, Father.

1386
00:57:24,808 --> 00:57:25,909
It's clear this experiment

1387
00:57:25,909 --> 00:57:27,678
is grossly out of control.

1388
00:57:27,678 --> 00:57:28,645
With all due respect,

1389
00:57:28,645 --> 00:57:30,580
Your Grace, I think it's out

1390
00:57:30,580 --> 00:57:32,082
of our control.

1391
00:57:32,082 --> 00:57:34,951
Sister Teresa is inspiring

1392
00:57:34,951 --> 00:57:36,586
young women to give selflessly

1393
00:57:36,586 --> 00:57:37,854
to those who need service

1394
00:57:37,854 --> 00:57:41,091
the most.

1395
00:57:41,091 --> 00:57:42,859
Why would these young girls,

1396
00:57:42,859 --> 00:57:43,760
who have their whole life

1397
00:57:43,760 --> 00:57:45,028
ahead of them,

1398
00:57:45,028 --> 00:57:48,198
give up everything to work for--

1399
00:57:48,198 --> 00:57:49,800
To work for what?

1400
00:57:49,800 --> 00:57:51,101
I believe they think

1401
00:57:51,101 --> 00:57:52,903
they are working for our Lord,

1402
00:57:52,903 --> 00:57:55,072
Jesus Christ.

1403
00:57:55,072 --> 00:57:57,607
For her own safety,

1404
00:57:57,607 --> 00:57:58,842
and for the welfare

1405
00:57:58,842 --> 00:58:00,143
of those girls,

1406
00:58:00,143 --> 00:58:02,079
I think we ought to insist

1407
00:58:02,079 --> 00:58:03,013
that Sister Teresa

1408
00:58:03,013 --> 00:58:04,581
return to Loreto.

1409
00:58:04,581 --> 00:58:05,549
I beg you, Your Grace,

1410
00:58:05,549 --> 00:58:06,817
let her complete her year.

1411
00:58:06,817 --> 00:58:08,185
At least let her do that.

1412
00:58:14,624 --> 00:58:15,325
Good morning.

1413
00:58:15,325 --> 00:58:16,193
Good morning.

1414
00:58:16,193 --> 00:58:17,094
Good morning, Mabel.

1415
00:58:17,094 --> 00:58:18,295
Hope you slept well.

1416
00:58:18,295 --> 00:58:19,196
Good morning, Maria.

1417
00:58:19,196 --> 00:58:20,330
A letter arrived for you.

1418
00:58:20,330 --> 00:58:22,632
Thank you.

1419
00:58:29,339 --> 00:58:31,074
Are you okay?

1420
00:58:31,074 --> 00:58:32,676
I wrote to my parents

1421
00:58:32,676 --> 00:58:34,845
to try to explain.

1422
00:58:34,845 --> 00:58:36,813
They didn't even open it.

1423
00:58:38,915 --> 00:58:40,751
We are your family now.

1424
00:58:44,254 --> 00:58:45,722
There are plenty of people

1425
00:58:45,722 --> 00:58:46,957
in Loreto who will welcome you

1426
00:58:46,957 --> 00:58:48,258
back at the end of the year.

1427
00:58:48,258 --> 00:58:50,026
The only problem is,

1428
00:58:50,026 --> 00:58:51,061
you've got these young girls

1429
00:58:51,061 --> 00:58:52,362
involved.

1430
00:58:52,362 --> 00:58:53,230
Why should there be

1431
00:58:53,230 --> 00:58:54,664
a problem?

1432
00:58:54,664 --> 00:58:56,233
They live by strict rules,

1433
00:58:56,233 --> 00:58:57,167
and as religious women,

1434
00:58:57,167 --> 00:58:58,034
even though they're not

1435
00:58:58,034 --> 00:58:59,069
nuns yet.

1436
00:58:59,069 --> 00:59:00,137
Yes, they're well into

1437
00:59:00,137 --> 00:59:01,838
their training as postulants.

1438
00:59:01,838 --> 00:59:03,807
And when you disband,

1439
00:59:03,807 --> 00:59:04,808
they'll be able to become

1440
00:59:04,808 --> 00:59:06,710
novitiates of the Loreto Order.

1441
00:59:06,710 --> 00:59:08,245
Disbanding?

1442
00:59:08,245 --> 00:59:10,213
What about the work?

1443
00:59:10,213 --> 00:59:11,214
We can't just abandon

1444
00:59:11,214 --> 00:59:13,316
these people we are helping.

1445
00:59:13,316 --> 00:59:15,085
But what are you going to do?

1446
00:59:15,085 --> 00:59:17,788
Father, I'm going to apply

1447
00:59:17,788 --> 00:59:19,055
for recognition

1448
00:59:19,055 --> 00:59:21,158
as a congregation.

1449
00:59:21,158 --> 00:59:23,093
(scoffs) The Vatican hasn't

1450
00:59:23,093 --> 00:59:24,628
authorized a new congregation

1451
00:59:24,628 --> 00:59:26,663
since 1850.

1452
00:59:26,663 --> 00:59:27,731
They'll say your work can be

1453
00:59:27,731 --> 00:59:28,899
taken over by lay people.

1454
00:59:28,899 --> 00:59:30,267
