01:00:49,179 --> 01:00:50,480
I did read these documents,

1495
01:00:50,480 --> 01:00:53,350
Father.

1496
01:00:53,350 --> 01:00:56,119
I leave for Rome next month.

1497
01:00:56,119 --> 01:00:57,254
If, in the interim, I hear no

1498
01:00:57,254 --> 01:00:58,889
negative reports of Sister

