01:00:58,889 --> 01:01:01,291
Teresa's work...

1500
01:01:01,291 --> 01:01:02,726
I'll take this application

1501
01:01:02,726 --> 01:01:03,460
with me.

1502
01:01:03,460 --> 01:01:05,161
But Your Grace, I...

1503
01:01:05,161 --> 01:01:06,463
Oh, you mean you--

1504
01:01:06,463 --> 01:01:09,232
I mean, I--

1505
01:01:09,232 --> 01:01:10,300
Thank you, Your Grace.

1506
01:01:10,300 --> 01:01:12,102
Thank you.

1507
01:01:12,102 --> 01:01:14,237
(bells tolling)

1508
01:01:21,778 --> 01:01:23,079
We are careful not to breathe

1509
