01:02:34,017 --> 01:02:35,385
They give you permission to run

1543
01:02:35,385 --> 01:02:36,486
amok in Calcutta,

1544
01:02:36,486 --> 01:02:37,554
and I am the one who has

1545
01:02:37,554 --> 01:02:38,555
to clean up the disaster.

1546
01:02:38,555 --> 01:02:41,224
Just like in Moti Jihl.

1547
01:02:41,224 --> 01:02:42,525
I thought that you and I had

1548
01:02:42,525 --> 01:02:43,927
