But where do you begin?

1579
01:03:36,179 --> 01:03:38,348
One.

1580
01:03:38,348 --> 01:03:39,983
That's where I am beginning.

1581
01:03:39,983 --> 01:03:43,219
One, then two, then three.

1582
01:03:43,219 --> 01:03:44,320
Already we have reached

1583
01:03:44,320 --> 01:03:45,288
more than a hundred.

1584
01:03:45,288 --> 01:03:46,389
And now you are seeking

1585
01:03:46,389 --> 01:03:47,524
permission to move into

1586
01:03:47,524 --> 01:03:48,558
the pilgrims' hostel.

1587
01:03:48,558 --> 01:03:51,127
It has two sleeping rooms.

1588
01:03:51,127 --> 01:03:52,529
It has electricity.

1589
01:03:52,529 --> 01:03:56,232
It has connections for cooking.

1590
01:03:56,232 --> 01:03:57,500
I am not interested in its

1591
01:03:57,500 --> 01:03:59,502
