1597
01:04:08,311 --> 01:04:09,913
Oh, I don't bring politics

1598
01:04:09,913 --> 01:04:11,481
into charity, Mr. Commissioner.

1599
01:04:11,481 --> 01:04:14,017
Sister! You are not the only

1600
01:04:14,017 --> 01:04:16,486
kind-hearted person in Calcutta.

1601
01:04:16,486 --> 01:04:19,255
You think no one else cares?

1602
01:04:19,255 --> 01:04:22,292
This is my city, and every day

1603
01:04:22,292 --> 01:04:24,127
I am brokenhearted to see our

1604
01:04:24,127 --> 01:04:25,995
people dying in the streets.

1605
01:04:25,995 --> 01:04:29,065
But for me, they're victims--

1606
01:04:29,065 --> 01:04:30,600
victims of colonialism

1607
01:04:30,600 --> 01:04:34,237
