1638
01:06:34,457 --> 01:06:35,825
Mrs. Goma.

1639
01:06:35,825 --> 01:06:36,826
I'm used to waiting for

1640
01:06:36,826 --> 01:06:38,228
Sister Teresa.

1641
01:06:38,228 --> 01:06:40,129
Ah, here she is,

1642
01:06:40,129 --> 01:06:43,066
