1657
01:07:09,525 --> 01:07:11,160
And to accept invitation only

1658
01:07:11,160 --> 01:07:12,595
from the wealthy would offend

1659
01:07:12,595 --> 01:07:13,830
the poor, so better say no

1660
01:07:13,830 --> 01:07:16,499
to everyone.

1661
01:07:16,499 --> 01:07:18,134
I'm sure that must frustrate

1662
01:07:18,134 --> 01:07:20,837
