1663
01:07:20,837 --> 01:07:22,705
Oh, I don't worry.

1664
01:07:22,705 --> 01:07:24,540
Mother Teresa?

1665
01:07:26,576 --> 01:07:28,778
(laughs)

1666
01:07:42,258 --> 01:07:45,328
Desperate, the lost,

1667
01:07:45,328 --> 01:07:47,497
the outcast.

