01:07:47,497 --> 01:07:49,499
Taking care of them,

1669
01:07:49,499 --> 01:07:51,768
rendering help to them,

1670
01:07:51,768 --> 01:07:53,770
visiting them assiduously,

1671
01:07:53,770 --> 01:07:56,839
living Christ's love for them,

1672
01:07:56,839 --> 01:07:58,708
and awakening their response

1673
01:07:58,708 --> 01:08:01,377
to His great love.

1674
01:08:01,377 --> 01:08:03,680
Amen.

1675
01:08:03,680 --> 01:08:04,814
God has triumphed through

1676
01:08:04,814 --> 01:08:07,650
you, Reverend Mother Teresa.

1677
01:08:07,650 --> 01:08:10,853
Welcome to the Calcutta diocese.

1678
01:08:12,722 --> 01:08:14,590
Just Mother Teresa,

1679
01:08:14,590 --> 01:08:16,359
Your Grace.

