Sheltering the abandoned,

1693
01:09:16,786 --> 01:09:19,389
caring for the unwanted,

1694
01:09:19,389 --> 01:09:21,457
unloved and lonely,

1695
01:09:21,457 --> 01:09:24,260
living Christ's love in our

1696
01:09:24,260 --> 01:09:26,863
spiritual work of mercy.

1697
01:09:26,863 --> 01:09:29,265
(overlapping chatter)

1698
01:09:37,774 --> 01:09:39,742
Sister Gertrude.

1699
01:09:39,742 --> 01:09:40,910
We have been looking

1700
01:09:40,910 --> 01:09:42,011
